b"Cont... Lou's unexpected, ice-breaking humor.  Lou's presence. BF"
b'RT "@killermuses Favorite memory working with Lou Reed???" Lou doing Tai Chi with Ron.  Lou admonishing me to write more...'
b'RT "@Lisamarie087896 Would the killers ever do a duet with a girl?" We have. Toni Halliday.  A Great Big Sled. BF'
b'Cont... After Ryan Pardey, . . . Eddie Murphy. RV'
b'RT: @AnsteyBray you\'ve made singles with @ryanpardey, M83 (@m83news) & Lou Reed. Who is your dream artist to make a single with?" After'
b'Cont... but hearing ZZ Top on the radio was a close second. RV'

b'RT "@DJHarleyQuinn Do you see Wembley as closing a chapter or starting a new tradition?" Just the beginning. RV'
b'RT "@SilvitaG67 From Battle Born, which of the songs took you more time to get finished and ready for the album?" Runaways was a doosie. RV'

b'RT "@ShimmyAndShake2 how is the decision made on what songs will be made singles? You guys, or the label?" Us. BF'
b'RT "@Nim_Nim11 what can you not live without when you go on tour? However small or big?" Cereal. The small ones. RV'

b'RT "@_Ju_Liette If you weren\'t in The Killers, what would be your job?" Valet parker. BF'
b'RT "@hotfuss_TK who had the idea of calling your fans "victims"?" They did. BF'

b'RT "@Neon_Tiger2015 What was your favorite subject in school?" Home Ec. Finding a girl who could cook was easier. RV'
b'RT "@AndreaRoseH What\'s the worse musical advice you\'ve ever been given?" To shelve Miss Atomic Bomb. RV'
